# Maintainer-only paths excluded from `git archive` (the adopter distribution).
# Affects ONLY git archive / scripts/adopter-export.sh — never the kit's own tree or CI.
# Link-safety: no KEPT doc has a `](path)` markdown link to any entry (S3 spec §4.1). Links
# BETWEEN export-ignored entries (ignored→ignored) are fine — both ends are pruned together;
# adopter-export-wired.sh enforces this by excluding the IGN set from its kept-doc link scan.
docs/ROADMAP-KIT.md                 export-ignore
.github/workflows/ci.yml            export-ignore
.github/workflows/ratification.yml  export-ignore
.github/workflows/release-coherence.yml export-ignore
.github/workflows/drift-watch.yml   export-ignore
.github/workflows/golden-path.yml   export-ignore
.github/dependabot.yml              export-ignore
docs/superpowers/                   export-ignore
.superpowers/                       export-ignore
.github/CODEOWNERS                                                export-ignore
docs/architecture/                  export-ignore
# docs/plans/ is TRACKED (Slice 3 moved plans out of gitignored docs/superpowers/ so a cold adopter
# can commit one) but maintainer-INTERNAL, like docs/architecture/. Without this, the first plan doc
# to live there took `adopter-export-wired` from green to red: a KEPT doc may not markdown-link an
# export-ignored target, and plans necessarily cite ci.yml / golden-path.yml / design docs.
# Safe w.r.t. Slice 3: orchestrator-loop-wired's check_plan_location asserts the location is not
# GITIGNORED — export-ignore does not untrack, so the plan is still committable by an adopter.
docs/plans/                         export-ignore
docs/governance/meta-control-log.md                              export-ignore
docs/governance/.meta-control-last                              export-ignore
BACKLOG.md                                                       export-ignore
KIT-FEEDBACK.md                                                  export-ignore
SPARKWRIGHT-CONSOLIDATED-BACKLOG.md                              export-ignore
ROADMAP.md                                                       export-ignore
CHANGELOG.md                                                     export-ignore
.publish-identifiers                                             export-ignore
scratchpad/                            export-ignore
scratchpad/**                          export-ignore
